{"tid":2426642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范徐麗泰：座談會提及立法會應改為至少10選區","createTime":"2021-02-28T08:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T09:34:38.000Z","uid":892,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbfa71fbc509f1affa58baec7fb36c59eaa1898","tid":2426642,"uid":892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"范徐麗泰：座談會提及立法會應改為至少10選區<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦主任夏寶龍在深圳主持座談會，與會的前全國人大常委范徐麗泰表示，會上談及選委會由愛國愛港人士出任，將來所有參加立法會選舉的候選人，提名人當中，應有若干名選委成員，才能保障當選者都是愛國愛港人士。范徐麗泰認為，現時立法會的比例代表制，只有5個選區，令選區太大，部分未能取得10%選票的參選人，也可以成為立法會議員，以致認受性不足，建議應將立法會的選區最少劃分為10區，又說雙議席單票制的建議，是可行的方法。范徐麗泰又表示，會上談及應取消立法會5個超級區議會議席。<br />\n<br />\n2021-02-28 15:39:56"},{"pid":"8eee0ff5315b46b8ba2ec95ca7369b791998f84b","tid":2426642,"uid":29784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"年年尾席都建制咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce902e4ba2db2369ab5135d5baf96183103c9e1","tid":2426642,"uid":85127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"方便配票 其實都無人理架啦 <br />\n你地鍾意點選就點選啦<br />\n大家有得移民就好移民<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chan-06_KpAb8_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchan-06_KpAb8_1200x0.png&h=659a8c47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890d51078ed35e2e0aebe06e294edd34dcca0f66","tid":2426642,"uid":22054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8eee0ff5315b46b8ba2ec95ca7369b791998f84b","tid":2426642,"uid":29784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"年年尾席都建制咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /