a-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchan-06_KpAb8_1200x0.png&h=659a8c47&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:52:42.000Z","msg":"到時唔洗配，40% vs 60% 直選都只會係55波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"點會55波 到時要幾多票咪有幾多票 鍾意有20萬票 咪整個20萬票箱比你lor<br />\n訓左幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"呢個係舞弊，唔係配票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢propse緊每區只選兩個位，名單制，最多票果兩張名單先有份玩第二輪點票，之後除非某張名單得票多過令一張一倍飛 (60%或以上 vs 30%或以下)，否則都係一人一席<br />\n<br />\nPS: 如果60% vs 31% 飛都係 一人一席，總之少數派搶1%，多數就要搶2%票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd86d7435eff95075aefb4dfdc15f915f0d7dce0","tid":2426642,"uid":85127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ac27799ed8a8fdae46f4d41f5d20cf7588d463","tid":2426642,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1967847aa8fb9620b7f70c7e9b4ef553911f44c","tid":2426642,"uid":85127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d66b84a6fefe8f0904b98dd726ca5372a17420c","tid":2426642,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:52:42.000Z","msg":"到時唔洗配，40% vs 60% 直選都只會係55波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"點會55波 到時要幾多票咪有幾多票 鍾意有20萬票 咪整個20萬票箱比你lor<br />\n訓左幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"呢個係舞弊，唔係配票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢propse緊每區只選兩個位，名單制，最多票果兩張名單先有份玩第二輪點票，之後除非某張名單得票多過令一張一倍飛 (60%或以上 vs 30%或以下)，否則都係一人一席<br />\n<br />\nPS: 如果60% vs 31% 飛都係 一人一席，總之少數派搶1%，多數就要搶2%票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"舞弊？ WFC？ICAC？掌心雷？一屋十幾姓？派錢投票？<br />\n<br />\n分散選區既好處係無連鎖效應，<br />\n例如九龍區A擺明垃圾廢老區，贏硬，唔使配<br />\n九龍區B多後生，就配，<br />\n有需要就配，無需要就唔使配，慢慢煮熟你，溫水煮蛙呢招用左幾十年，由頭用到落尾，熟曬架步。<br />\n至於點配票，立法會，區議會咁多DATA 做analysis，根本無任何難度。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，反正都無人可以選，你覺得點選仲重要咩？"},{"pid":"fc7d0d0186ef38b14296572394eced8c4fc4ce60","tid":2426642,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d102396a6158a8580a20fb63dfea6e562c9a185","tid":2426642,"uid":47384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:52:03.000Z","msg":"屌 人都比你拉哂 搵鬼選咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"因為可以搵個白底素人去選<br />\n只要唔係共狗都會贏"},{"pid":"ad556be36ea1802fae2f331098adbb586b632acb","tid":2426642,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd86d7435eff95075aefb4dfdc15f915f0d7dce0","tid":2426642,"uid":85127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ac27799ed8a8fdae46f4d41f5d20cf7588d463","tid":2426642,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1967847aa8fb9620b7f70c7e9b4ef553911f44c","tid":2426642,"uid":85127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"點會55波 到時要幾多票咪有幾多票 鍾意有20萬票 咪整個20萬票箱比你lor<br />\n訓左幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"